downgrade the ubuntu system : ------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    Ubuntu Groovy 20.10
    Ubuntu Focal 20.04 (LTS)
    Ubuntu Bionic 18.04 (LTS)
    Ubuntu Xenial 16.04 (LTS)

to downgrade from Groovy to Focal 
 sudo sed -i 's/groovy/focal/g' /etc/apt/sources.list
 
 edit or create /etc/apt/preferences
 
 complete details : 
Package: *
Pin: release a=focal
Pin-Priority: 1001

finally : 
$ sudo apt update
$ sudo apt upgrade
$ sudo apt dist-upgrade

***********************************************************************************************************************************
check ubuntu version : cat /etc/*release*

